    <analysis_type>MA-XRF</analysis_type>
    <analysis_title>MA-XRF mapping of Giovanni Bellini's Adoration of the Magi</analysis_title>
    <notes>Macro X-ray fluorescence mapping campaign carried out on the Adoration of the Magi by Giovanni Bellini, part of the permanent collection of the Pinacoteca di Brera. The campaign aimed to characterise the pigment palette and painting technique, with particular attention to underdrawing and pentimenti revealed by elemental distribution maps. The analysis was performed during a scheduled conservation assessment at the Laboratorio di Restauro della Pinacoteca di Brera. Several scan sessions were required to achieve full surface coverage.</notes>
